caption: The image depicts a group of people riding camels under a night sky. The scene is set against a backdrop of a crescent moon and stars. The people are arranged in a line, with some riding closer to the front and others further back. The camels are spread out, with some positioned closer to the left side of the image and others towards the right. The overall atmosphere of the image suggests a sense of adventure and exploration, as the group travels together under the night sky.
original_title: Minimalist Cream Illustration Al Isra Wal Miraj Islamic Instagram Story
texts:
On this day of Isra Mi'raj, hopefully we can become
better human beings and can take lessons
